हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Ordinary laborer Yash is suddenly gifted with extraordinary strength, turning him into a local legend. But admiration turns to betrayal when his girlfriend Tanya schemes to steal his family’s secret formula. With his mentor in danger, Yash must rise — not just with power, but with purpose — to reclaim his honor.
